{"tid":731650,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"西醫咁多副作用 ，憑咩話自己先進和屌替代醫學","createTime":"2018-07-06T11:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T04:42:51.000Z","uid":149978,"like":16,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8961f96fe8f27463dbb84ad4061e42375bdece","tid":731650,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"成日話替代醫學（即另類治療，包括中醫、針灸、脊醫、自然療法、信仰治療）係偽科學和偽醫學。<br />\n<br />\n但無視自己西醫的副作用多到 hihi。<br />\n又有一大推病係醫唔到，冇藥醫。"},{"pid":"3243b74e700324df1316179f7242134c5b84778a","tid":731650,"uid":2771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:11:19.000Z","msg":"又敗走？"},{"pid":"c87211751e623178686b332d841e011dfc58ef92","tid":731650,"uid":30510,"like":43,"dislike":11,"score":32,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"有副作用都好過中醫完全無作用"},{"pid":"7ad926fd0517158f465c4294f6ca088869a4ee78","tid":731650,"uid":51229,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:13:05.000Z","msg":"有副作用同偽科學有咩關係？<br />\n一個就有齊數據 知道晒效用同副作用<br />\n一個就乜都唔知 最緊要信"},{"pid":"374877897d761b8c5d36acb09ffe5f4f4a2ae030","tid":731650,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"c87211751e623178686b332d841e011dfc58ef92","tid":731650,"uid":30510,"like":43,"dislike":11,"score":32,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"有副作用都好過中醫完全無作用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"咁就唔好話自己先進咪得lor，<br />\n憑咩話現代醫學先進？"},{"pid":"c0728afeb31004c7476abdc13a7199b1a62d26da","tid":731650,"uid":9115,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:14:16.000Z","msg":"根本西醫就係垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377bf396ea110143b796ca8457ad3234473006db","tid":731650,"uid":51021,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ad926fd0517158f465c4294f6ca088869a4ee78","tid":731650,"uid":51229,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:13:05.000Z","msg":"有副作用同偽科學有咩關係？<br />\n